philosophy-reverse-engineering:
    "Philosophy is the <i>reverse engineering</i> of the Universe. System analysis can happen at several levels, from the user interface down to binary code. Analyzing at low levels is harder and leads, at best, to knowledge of the operating mechanics, not of the business rules."

